Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.49,0:01:34.29,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Ichigo agrees to become\Nthe bodyguard for
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.33,0:01:37.31,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Princess Rurichiyo of the Kasumiohji Clan,\Na high ranking noble family.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.85,0:01:40.34,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,And now he must battle \Nthe assassins sent
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.34,0:01:44.27,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,by Gyokaku Kumoi, who \Nplots to take over.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.33,0:01:48.21,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Kumoi gives the assassins\Nthe Bakkouto,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.25,0:01:52.45,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,which are made through\Nsecret Kasumiohji techniques,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.49,0:01:54.01,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,and they attack Ichigo and his
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.01,0:01:56.26,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,comrades with their special powers.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.97,0:02:01.29,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,In the face of their\Npowerful Bakkouto,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.33,0:02:04.27,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,one assassin's Spiritual Pressure\Nis completely exhausted,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.27,0:02:07.69,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,another is unable to\Nunleash its full power,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.69,0:02:10.69,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,and they are all\Nultimately defeated.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.25,0:02:44.62,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Lord Kannogi.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.16,0:02:47.10,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,That certainly becomes you.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.76,0:02:50.48,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Tell me…\NIs Ruricchi really coming?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.72,0:02:53.38,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I don’t want to go through\Nthe wedding ceremony alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.88,0:02:55.77,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Please do not worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.48,0:02:59.17,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Princess Rurichiyo will\Nmost certainly return
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.17,0:03:00.69,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,before the ceremony.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.60,0:03:04.90,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Really? You seem\Nconfident about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.52,0:03:08.24,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I am. So do not worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.49,0:03:13.78,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Wedding ceremony?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.60,0:03:15.40,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.68,0:03:18.94,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,The wedding preparations are\Ncontinuing in the Kasumiohji Clan
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.94,0:03:21.15,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,for Rurichiyo and Shu Kannogi.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.55,0:03:24.01,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Who is this Kannogi?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.69,0:03:28.12,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Sir Shu is Lady Rurichiyo’s fiancé.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.12,0:03:31.87,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Fiancé? She has\Nsomeone like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.31,0:03:34.59,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,That’s the aristocracy for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.72,0:03:37.56,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,There is talk that Shu Kannogi
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.56,0:03:42.03,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,has already been installed as\Nthe head of the Kasumiohji Clan.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.03,0:03:47.41,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,So now, they’ll rush through\Nthe ceremony and make it official.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.60,0:03:52.04,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,But Rurichiyo is with us.\NHow can they get married?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.04,0:03:54.82,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,A stand-in, perhaps.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.82,0:04:00.02,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,After all, most people won’t\Nknow the difference.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.29,0:04:04.40,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Prominent nobles of Soul Society\Nwill receive invitations.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.82,0:04:06.37,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,On the day of the marriage,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.37,0:04:08.67,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,the gates of the Kasumiohji \NClan will open,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.67,0:04:13.50,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,so that the common people\Ncan get a glimpse of the bride.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.68,0:04:18.97,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,They’re taking all the steps necessary\Nto thwart our actions!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.24,0:04:23.17,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,That Kumoi…\NHe resorted to such dirty tactics!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.20,0:04:26.37,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,When is the ceremony scheduled?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.92,0:04:28.15,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,The day after tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.88,0:04:31.04,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,So there’s a little time.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.47,0:04:34.37,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Which means he may try to lure us into
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.37,0:04:37.23,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,a trap and take Princess Rurichiyo back.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.56,0:04:39.12,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,That’s a possibility.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.16,0:04:41.55,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,He’s controlling the situation and
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.55,0:04:43.55,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,minimizing the actions we can take,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.55,0:04:45.62,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,driving us into a corner.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.20,0:04:50.07,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,We can’t make any move freely.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.60,0:04:54.39,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Inoue is doing her best\Nwith Ishida and Sado,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.39,0:04:56.15,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,but the enemy’s evil \NSpiritual Pressure
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.15,0:04:57.97,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,lingers around the wound openings.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.97,0:05:01.01,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,It’s taking time for her to reject it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.44,0:05:06.48,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,This sword… Did you say\Nit was called a Bakkouto?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.42,0:05:08.45,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.56,0:05:12.52,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,It’s a sword that \Neats up the wielder’s
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.52,0:05:14.43,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Spirit Energy and converts it to power.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.43,0:05:20.61,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Kisuke…\NYou aren’t familiar with it either?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.88,0:05:24.20,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I hope you don’t think\NI know everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.28,0:05:27.76,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,What is it, Enryu?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.12,0:05:39.18,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,No… Lady Rurichiyo isn’t here.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.36,0:05:44.32,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,How can you tell from just that?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.84,0:05:57.15,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Lady Rurichiyo.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.92,0:06:00.76,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,So here you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.84,0:06:09.36,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Don’t worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.84,0:06:14.62,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Let’s leave it to Orihime Inoue.\NThey will recover fully.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.08,0:06:20.94,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Now…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.94,0:06:23.27,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,We must not get in the way.\NLet us leave.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.16,0:06:26.41,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Lady Rurichiyo?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.26,0:06:30.04,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,It’s all right, Rurichiyo.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.84,0:06:35.64,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I know!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.88,0:06:40.38,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Rurichiyo, can you help me\Nwring out the towels?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.38,0:06:41.27,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.22,0:06:44.15,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,All right? Please?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.26,0:06:54.47,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Please use this.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.24,0:07:12.58,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you, Rurichiyo.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.51,0:07:14.55,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I am sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.84,0:07:15.58,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.27,0:07:19.76,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I am so helpless.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.49,0:07:21.98,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,That’s not true!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.98,0:07:24.19,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,This wasn’t your fault, Rurichiyo!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.72,0:07:44.54,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,So here you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.06,0:07:55.09,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,They say something and\Nsmoke like high places.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.40,0:08:00.23,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,You were on the roof\Nthe last time too.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.24,0:08:02.56,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I had forgotten.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.06,0:08:12.37,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Ishida and Chad didn’t get hurt\Nbecause of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.92,0:08:14.00,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Don’t worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.40,0:08:16.41,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,You are wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.41,0:08:17.64,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,No, I’m not.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.60,0:08:19.91,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,You are wrong!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.91,0:08:21.98,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,If I were not here, they would not
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.98,0:08:23.63,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,-have gone through such suffering.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.98,0:08:23.63,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,-You’re wrong!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.84,0:08:26.44,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,They didn’t come after you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.76,0:08:30.19,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,After all, that Nukui guy\Ncame to fight me personally.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.92,0:08:33.16,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.44,0:08:34.04,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.63,0:08:38.54,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Even I know that\Nthey were not bandits!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.08,0:08:41.24,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Kumoi sent them!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.86,0:08:44.64,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Kumoi wants to take over\Nthe Kasumiohji Clan,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.64,0:08:47.61,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,and he wants me dead!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.72,0:08:51.11,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Rurichiyo, you…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.16,0:08:57.58,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I have known that Kumoi\Nwas after me for a long time.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.38,0:09:01.28,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I also know that you all kept quiet
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.28,0:09:02.89,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,so that I would not worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.23,0:09:06.92,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I am very grateful for that.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.23,0:09:09.79,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,But… But…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.56,0:09:12.56,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Rurichiyo…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.08,0:09:16.50,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,We all made the decision on our own\Nand chose to protect you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.35,0:09:20.36,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,None of us could\Nignore your dilemma.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.45,0:09:25.34,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Besides,\NI’m a Substitute Soul Reaper!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.79,0:09:28.03,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,It’s part of my job \Nto keep people like you
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.03,0:09:30.45,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,from wandering around.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.12,0:09:33.28,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Ichigo…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.08,0:09:37.05,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,So don’t cry!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.12,0:09:39.39,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I am not crying!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.35,0:09:42.15,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,We’ll be all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.88,0:09:46.55,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Ishida and Chad may take \Nmore time to recover,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.55,0:09:48.37,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,but Inoue will do something.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.20,0:09:50.83,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,So don’t worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.72,0:09:55.07,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you, Ichigo.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.40,0:10:02.21,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.21,0:10:03.68,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,What’re you doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.16,0:10:08.24,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Forgive me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.48,0:10:16.56,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Unlock!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.56,0:10:17.88,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Oww…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.34,0:10:25.37,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Rurichiyo!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.96,0:10:28.84,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I am grateful for your effort.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.00,0:10:32.86,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,However, I cannot trouble\Nyou all any further!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.32,0:10:37.05,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I will take action myself and\Ntake back the Kasumiohji Clan!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.84,0:10:39.02,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Rurichiyo!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.62,0:10:40.78,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,What’s wrong, Ichigo?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.78,0:10:42.22,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,What happened?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.29,0:10:44.19,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.52,0:10:45.95,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Lady Rurichiyo!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.00,0:10:51.04,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,What’s the meaning of this,\NIchigo Kurosaki?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.04,0:10:53.52,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I’ll explain later!\NWe’re going after her!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.48,0:11:01.23,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,What’re you doing?!\NHurry and open the Senkaimon!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.23,0:11:02.65,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I know that!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.68,0:11:06.58,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Unlock!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.52,0:11:08.32,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.68,0:11:09.58,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.72,0:11:10.68,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,What’s the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.68,0:11:12.36,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,The gate won’t open.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.64,0:11:14.18,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,What does that mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.18,0:11:19.46,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Lady Rurichiyo has locked it\Nfrom the other side. I’m sure of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.64,0:11:22.18,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn’t there a way to open it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.18,0:11:23.99,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Without a key, it’s useless!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.99,0:11:25.13,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.12,0:11:26.02,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Ichigo!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.88,0:11:28.32,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Think about the situation.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.56,0:11:32.39,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,If you use that gate,\Nyou’ll only fall into the enemy’s trap!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.64,0:11:34.94,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Then what do you\Nexpect us to do?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.94,0:11:36.64,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Calm down, Ichigo!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.44,0:11:42.61,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Why did Princess Rurichiyo\Ndecide to return to her clan?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.60,0:11:49.09,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,She knew that Kumoi\Nwas targeting her.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.09,0:11:50.00,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.96,0:11:55.99,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,And she blamed herself for\Neverything that’s happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.56,0:11:57.91,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh no!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.91,0:11:59.81,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,So that’s it, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.10,0:12:03.53,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,But what does she plan to do\Nby returning all on her own?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.76,0:12:04.64,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Could it be?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.80,0:12:07.69,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,She intends to subdue Kumoi\Nby proceeding with the marriage
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.69,0:12:10.05,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,and taking over\Nas the head of the clan!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.05,0:12:12.51,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,They’re not that naïve!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.12,0:12:14.10,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Rukia!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.10,0:12:15.92,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Open your Senkaimon!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.40,0:12:17.37,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.16,0:12:22.32,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Unlock!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.98,0:12:31.20,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Kurosaki!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.92,0:12:34.26,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Be careful.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.40,0:12:36.83,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Inoue, look after Ishida and Chad!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.12,0:12:38.07,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Let’s go!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.25,0:12:44.80,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,So they’re off.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.16,0:12:49.05,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, knowing Kurosaki,\NI expected that much.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.56,0:12:52.28,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,However, the opponent\Nis a high-ranking noble.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.04,0:12:55.23,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,It won’t be that easy.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.91,0:13:17.91,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Princess!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.59,0:13:21.85,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,The princess has returned!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.95,0:13:23.39,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,What?! The princess?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.63,0:13:24.97,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,This is urgent!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.97,0:13:26.82,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,We must go out to greet her!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.67,0:13:28.77,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.77,0:13:30.02,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Princess?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.87,0:13:33.03,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,– Princess!\N– Princess!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.03,0:13:33.99,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome back.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.44,0:13:36.46,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,This is a relief.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.39,0:13:40.43,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome home,\NLady Rurichiyo.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.43,0:13:57.41,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Hold it!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.41,0:13:59.71,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I am Rukia Kuchiki of Squad 13.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.71,0:14:00.53,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,And the others?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.53,0:14:03.25,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,He is Substitute Soul Reaper\NIchigo Kurosaki.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.25,0:14:06.46,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,The others are Sir Kenryu and\NSir Enryu of the Kasumiohji Clan.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.46,0:14:08.31,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,We don’t have\Na request for passage.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.31,0:14:10.08,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Please wait while we verify this.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.08,0:14:11.51,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,We don’t have the time!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.51,0:14:13.93,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Hold on, Ichigo.\NWe must comply.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.71,0:14:31.82,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Ruricchi, you’re really back.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.03,0:14:35.53,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I became the lord\Nin your absence.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.79,0:14:36.79,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I’m sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.75,0:14:39.08,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,It matters not.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.41,0:14:42.26,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I have no desire to become\Nthe head of the clan.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.26,0:14:45.59,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,But we’ll be together from now on!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.59,0:14:47.53,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,What shall we do?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.53,0:14:49.77,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe cards or fan toss?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.11,0:14:53.98,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, you prefer handball,\Ndon’t you?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.64,0:15:04.46,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,How come it took so long\Nto pass through the Senkaimon?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.46,0:15:08.38,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,We tried to go through without a pass,\Nso it couldn’t be helped.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.64,0:15:11.12,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank goodness we\Ngot through without a hitch.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.94,0:15:13.94,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,The ceremony is tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.15,0:15:15.59,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,We’re running out of time.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.59,0:15:16.65,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.91,0:15:18.65,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,What will we do when\Nwe get to the mansion?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.95,0:15:21.32,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,We can’t create too much\Nof a disturbance.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.51,0:15:25.76,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Leave that to us!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.76,0:15:31.23,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I will get Lady Rurichiyo out.\NI am the chief chamberlain, after all!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.63,0:15:33.27,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that important?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.27,0:15:37.92,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Certainly! I am the top retainer\Namong the princess’s aides.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.15,0:15:40.67,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,So I’m able to enter freely!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.19,0:15:46.52,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Open the gate!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.07,0:15:48.79,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Chief Chamberlain of\Nthe Kasumiohji Clan,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.83,0:15:53.00,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Ryusei Kenzaki and\NRuzaburo Enkougawa wish to enter!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.07,0:15:55.97,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,You…had names like that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.39,0:15:58.94,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,What is the delay?!\NOpen the gates!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.99,0:16:07.37,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,What is the meaning of this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.37,0:16:12.47,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Silence! You two are suspected\Nof abducting Princess Rurichiyo!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.47,0:16:14.15,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Submit to arrest!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.48,0:16:17.02,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn…that Kumoi!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.64,0:16:19.86,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,We cannot allow ourselves\Nto be arrested here!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.86,0:16:20.93,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course not!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.93,0:16:22.52,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Then what’ll we do?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.52,0:16:23.49,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Well…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.11,0:16:28.11,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,We retreat for now!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.71,0:16:30.51,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.67,0:16:31.54,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,– Hold it!\N– Hold it!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.03,0:16:33.22,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Hold on!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.22,0:16:35.31,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, I thought you\Nwere a big shot!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.31,0:16:36.97,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Why run away?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.11,0:16:40.14,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,We’re not running away!\NWe’re falling back to regroup!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.45,0:16:42.01,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Same thing!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.01,0:16:44.98,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,– Hold it!\N– Hold it!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.67,0:16:46.47,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,This way!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.19,0:16:47.95,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,This way!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.26,0:16:51.52,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,– What's going on?\N– Where are they?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.52,0:16:52.83,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,– I don’t see them!\N– Where'd they go?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.83,0:16:55.26,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,– No way!\N– Find them!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.90,0:17:04.04,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,We gave them the slip.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.55,0:17:07.33,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I’m surprised you have\Na place like this prepared.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.63,0:17:10.79,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,This is commonplace in\Na noble’s mansion!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.27,0:17:12.82,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that so?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.43,0:17:14.34,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I don’t know.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.34,0:17:16.62,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,What will we do now?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.95,0:17:19.35,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,We can use\Nthe secret passages to get—
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.35,0:17:20.82,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,No, hold it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.95,0:17:23.03,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.87,0:17:30.53,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Judging from earlier, the entire mansion\Nseems to be under heavy guard.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.53,0:17:32.80,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,That’s because it’s the day\Nbefore the wedding ceremony.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.28,0:17:36.93,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Then rather than search blindly,\Nwe should wait until tomorrow,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.93,0:17:41.00,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,when we’ll know exactly\Nwhere Rurichiyo will be.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.40,0:17:43.19,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Wha—?!\NIf we did that, then—
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.19,0:17:44.47,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,No…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.47,0:17:46.51,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,That’s probably better.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.95,0:17:48.35,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,It will be an official event.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.35,0:17:51.98,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,For Lady Rurichiyo to openly order\NKumoi as the head of the clan.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.98,0:17:53.68,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,No one will be able to ignore her.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.41,0:17:58.47,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,In our efforts to protect her,\Nwe treated her like a child,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.47,0:18:00.16,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,and ended up pushing her\Ninto a corner.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.79,0:18:05.10,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,She endured so much,\Nand we couldn’t protect her.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.44,0:18:09.23,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Rurichiyo made up her mind\Nand came here.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.79,0:18:12.41,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,She wanted to confront\Nher destiny head on.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.23,0:18:17.07,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Well then,\NI say let’s wager on her resolve!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.15,0:18:22.05,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.75,0:18:26.14,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Kenryu, you can show us the way\Ninside the mansion, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.83,0:18:28.02,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,You can count on me!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.83,0:18:31.51,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait for us, Rurichiyo.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.66,0:20:04.87,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,The marriage ceremony of\Nthe 37th Lord of the Kasumiohji Clan,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.87,0:20:08.85,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Lord Shu Kannogi and\NPrincess Rurichiyo has been completed.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.77,0:20:26.00,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Lord Shu, the new lord\Nof the Kasumiohji Clan,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.00,0:20:28.54,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,and his bride, Princess Rurichiyo,\Nwill arrive shortly!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.85,0:20:32.03,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Stand in your place and wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.52,0:20:53.31,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Look at that, Ruricchi!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.31,0:20:57.94,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,They’re all rejoicing\Nover our marriage.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.29,0:21:03.29,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Rurichiyo!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.78,0:21:09.77,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Let’s go!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.64,0:21:16.09,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-Who are you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.65,0:21:17.85,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Intruders!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.05,0:21:20.42,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Intruders!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.81,0:21:23.39,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Rurichiyo! Listen to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.13,0:21:25.36,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?! What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.36,0:21:29.76,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Rurichiyo! Rurichiyo!\NIt’s me, Ichigo! Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.76,0:21:31.03,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,They’ve fallen into the trap.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.03,0:21:33.08,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,– Ruri—\N– That’s as far as you go, Ichigo Kurosaki!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.14,0:21:37.54,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Captain Soi Fon?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.29,0:21:41.08,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,W-What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.09,0:21:48.09,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Rurichiyo!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.48,0:23:22.77,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,In the documents we filled out\Nto pass through the Senkaimon,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.77,0:23:24.25,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,there was a line for a sponsor.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.64,0:23:25.95,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Who did you name?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.95,0:23:27.13,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,My brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.13,0:23:29.13,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,If anything happens,\Nhe’ll be put on the spot,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.13,0:23:30.20,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,so be careful.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.20,0:23:31.61,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway you look at it,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.61,0:23:33.34,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,it’s kind of obvious we’re going to\Ncause trouble for him this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.34,0:23:34.66,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Crap!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.74,0:23:43.03,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,There’s nothing to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.03,0:23:46.15,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Jeez, I’m tired of just lying\Naround doing nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.15,0:23:47.70,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,You guys!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.61,0:23:50.08,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,You’re too lax!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.08,0:23:51.89,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,They can call us up anytime!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.12,0:23:53.52,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Red Pineapple.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.86,0:23:55.88,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Who you calling Red Pineapple?!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.60,0:23:59.08,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I’m ready to show off\Nmy secret weapon anytime!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.80,0:24:02.05,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I can’t wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.05,0:24:05.02,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,– Man, I wanna pee!\N– Are you sure you guys are ready?